The crew of a Turkish airlines flight are being investigated after they allowed Turkish football team captain Arda Turan into the cockpit so he could use the tannoy to congratulate his team-mates .
He was celebrating after the team 's 2-1 international friendly victory against Luxembourg and had gone to the cockpit to announce his congratulations over the PA system .
Turkish aviation officials said it was a serious breach of the safety rules of the flight back from Luxembourg City .